y as has been proved with dozens of side-by-side tests.&nbsp; Place 1/4\" holes 2\" apart on all six sides and make sure you have the terrarium elevated off the table it's on so air can enter the bottom.<br />RR","title":"Re: A first time post, a first time grow, and one question!"}}